'''Facebook Messenger'''是一個提供文字和語音服務的即時通訊軟件／應用程式，於2011年8月9日發表，用戶可以透過網站或移動裝置向其他用戶傳送文字、圖片、[[動畫|動畫]]、[[語音|語音]]和[[短片|短片]]等[[多媒体|多媒体]]訊息（甚至進行[[語音|語音]]通話），而無需額外付費。於2014年11月，[[Facebook|Facebook]]表示，Facebook Messenger已有約12億用户。<ref name=washington-post-messenger>{{cite web |url=http://articles.washingtonpost.com/2013-01-17/business/36383982_1_facebook-messenger-facebook-phone-facebook-users |title=Facebook Messenger app change allows free calls via WiFi |first=Hayley |last=Tsukayama |publisher=The Washington Post |date=January 17, 2013 |accessdate=March 3, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130120191703/http://articles.washingtonpost.com/2013-01-17/business/36383982_1_facebook-messenger-facebook-phone-facebook-users |archive-date=2013-01-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="building facebook messenger">{{cite web |url=https://www.facebook.com/notes/facebook-engineering/building-facebook-messenger/10150259350998920 |title=Building Facebook Messenger |first=Lucy |last=Zhang |work=Facebook Engineering |publisher=[[Facebook|Facebook]] |date=August 12, 2011 |accessdate=March 3, 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819133800/https://www.facebook.com/notes/facebook-engineering/building-facebook-messenger/10150259350998920 |archive-date=2015-08-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

